{"tid":1616654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發，班加拿大佬踩上去政黨總部踩場，重奪加拿大議會陣線！","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T00:53:27.000Z","uid":23480,"like":106,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"f1bb8090683205e799631f35d638407eef6dbffb","tid":1616654,"uid":23480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"加拿大聯邦選舉戰線！公開信第二擊！<br />\n<br />\n公開信其實係較早時候已經透過email正式send去六大政黨，但係我地絕對唔放心單靠一封email去表達我地對各大政黨既表罷同立場。<br />\n<br />\n係10.1既早上，我地cansavehk既代表，直接踩上門，去到位於ottawa既自由黨、保守黨、新民主黨、綠黨既總部，正式面交我地既書面質詢，其中，自由黨、綠黨、新民主黨更有代表正式收信。保守黨更以書面確認接收我地既質詢。<br />\n<br />\ncansavehk團隊會密切跟進。<br />\n加港同行，加拿大人，與香港人同行到底。<br />\n<br />\n同場再次呼籲！一定一定要登記做選民，有票一定要去投！為左香港，我地一定唔可以再俾親共政黨上枱，我地要全面圍堵中國，係加拿大要打擊所以親共既政府力量，一票不投共產黨！大家一定要幫幫手，海外x香港，屌柒共產黨！<br />\n<br />\n時代革命，光復香港。<br />\nwe stand with hong kong.<br />\n<br />\n加拿大戰線要人, 加拿大戰線第二擊, 重奪加拿大國會, 選票救香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588663</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n老到連鄭大班都忍唔住出聲，我呼籲所有加拿大香港人，團結一致，屌柒共產黨！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JGGNUk0f6mk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJGGNUk0f6mk&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=f7faccce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JGGNUk0f6mk</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXztADF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXztADF.jpg&h=c5afb86d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKr7Rb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKr7Rb1.jpg&h=b30a4bce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3jWr6Ln.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3jWr6Ln.jpg&h=c022819b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VnPUwb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnPUwb3.jpg&h=26b2aa2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g0SCtYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg0SCtYK.jpg&h=ea3c8778&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Ju1VDL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Ju1VDL.jpg&h=56a80849&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80a382e1e20a7ca84e8eb9cd6d941984f5dd9c57","tid":1616654,"uid":194325,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:28:40.000Z","msg":"香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEi%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=89d2afca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"bc3a440d077a371f0c901e4e0109a7012214b5bb","tid":1616654,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:29:26.000Z","msg":"保守黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0645a31c55f3101c927027c8c1ced295b32d3eb","tid":1616654,"uid":264192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"cf7733f7b53f89363637582e772e6c463f387e37","tid":1616654,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:32:11.000Z","msg":"居港加人 幫忙"},{"pid":"85d96926e1266ba604ecb338ba0104469096a5e2","tid":1616654,"uid":233050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"92df30e9ea4c4d93111a2d85200e5dcfbda11a22","tid":1616654,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike